      <title>和解猜测推动 XRP 成为加密货币反弹的前沿</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/settlement-speculation-pushes-xrp-to-forefront-of-crypto-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一种鲜为人知的加密货币正处于行业一场关键法律斗争的焦点，而人们猜测其背后的公司可能很快与美国监管机构达成和解，因此引领了数字资产的最新一次上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/settlement-speculation-pushes-xrp-to-forefront-of-crypto-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 17:15:19 GMT</pubDate>
