      <title>道富银行出售优先股以增加回购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/state-street-sells-preferred-shares-amid-bid-to-beef-up-buybacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[道富银行 (State Street Corp.) 将于周三发行一系列新的优先股，就在前一天，该公司财务总监表示将加快股票回购步伐。]]></description>
